<br>
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-43_ pf-r pf-c-lm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-44_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-45_ pf-heading-1-h3">Relevant legislation, regulations, and best practice</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-47_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-48_ pf-text-1"><strong>Health and Safety at Work Act (1974)</strong> - Section 2 of this legislation places a legal duty on employers to provide adequate employee training, with clear learning objectives as a foundation for compliance.





























</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-50_ pf-text-1"><strong>Care Quality Commission (CQC) Standards</strong> - CQC regulations mandate healthcare providers to deliver training that meets specified standards, including establishing clear learning objectives to enhance patient safety and quality of care.







































</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-52_ pf-text-1"><strong>General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) </strong>- Compliance with GDPR necessitates training employees on data protection principles, with clearly defined learning objectives facilitating understanding and adherence to regulatory requirements.







































</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-54_ pf-r pf-c-lm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-55_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-56_ pf-heading-1-h3">Importance of clear learning objectives
