</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-61_ pf-text-1"><strong>Measurable outcomes</strong> - Well-defined objectives enable trainers to assess learning progress objectively, facilitating the measurement of training effectiveness and ROI.










































